w.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Ngh%E1%BB%87-An-chu-trung/poem-WVc5_imVDPOxq9FVEHjt6w">Nghệ An chu trung - 乂安舟中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%B4i-Ch%E1%BA%A5n/Th%C3%B4n-v%C3%A3n/poem-R29M1NBy8bDIY4oGRe_cTw">Thôn vãn - 村晚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%B4i-Ch%E1%BA%A5n/author-gMKoP4uA5v9xIyy7Zcy9Ew">Lôi Chấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-T%E1%BB%B1-Tr%C3%A2n/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD/poem-9nWCkWvY4e5ub3BlqmzbGQ">Vịnh sử - 詠史</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-T%E1%BB%B1-Tr%C3%A2n/author-7r72VrPQwdDMRtQY4fV6gg">Cung Tự Trân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/V%C5%A9-Doanh-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng/poem-ObjktjQV3nPI7afgmsJBUQ">Vũ Doanh động - 武盈洞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
